                            <comment id="13113536" author="danapsimer" created="Fri, 23 Sep 2011 16:29:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is a small fix for the super column issues.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13130850" author="brandon.williams" created="Wed, 19 Oct 2011 18:22:57 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Dana, can you rebase?  I can&apos;t get this to apply.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13183504" author="brandon.williams" created="Tue, 10 Jan 2012 19:34:17 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;v2 with a slightly different approach.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13197157" author="xedin" created="Tue, 31 Jan 2012 19:42:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;isSub = 2 lead to key_validator, it should be changed to 3. Wouldn&apos;t it be a good idea to set &apos;AbstractType comparator&apos; instead of &apos;boolean isSub&apos; in columnToTuple(...)?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13197189" author="xedin" created="Tue, 31 Jan 2012 20:25:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;v3 with implements proposed parameter change to AbstractType comparator and removes unnecessary &apos;ByteBuffer name&apos; parameter.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
